## BACKGROUND SERVICE WORKER

The background script handles:
1. Message passing from content scripts
2. API calls to the Fohlioo backend (content scripts cannot make cross-origin requests directly in MV3)
3. Tab tracking for tab_open_count
4. Session management

```typescript
// background.ts
chrome.runtime.onMessage.addListener((message, sender, sendResponse) => {
  if (message.type === "SEND_EVENT") {
    sendEventToApi(message.data)
      .then(() => sendResponse({ success: true }))
      .catch(err => sendResponse({ success: false, error: err.message }))
    return true // keep channel open for async response
  }
  
  if (message.type === "GET_TAB_COUNT") {
    chrome.tabs.query({}, tabs => {
      const fashionTabCount = tabs.filter(tab => 
        tab.url && isFashionSite(tab.url)
      ).length
      sendResponse({ count: fashionTabCount })
    })
    return true
  }
})
```

