## THE FOUR SHOPPER SEGMENTS

Always use these exact names and descriptions in code, copy, and UI.

### Investment Dresser
- Considers for 7-21 days before buying
- Dwell time P75 above 90 seconds
- Return rate under 12%
- Full price rate above 80%
- Average order value above £200
- Revisits same product 3-5 times
- Reads reviews and material sections

### Trend Chaser
- Session to purchase under 72 hours
- Purchases 2+ times per month
- Return rate 28-45%
- Over 50% of browsing on discounted items
- Dwell time P75 under 40 seconds
- Average order value under £160

### Quiet Minimalist
- Colour palette entropy under 0.3 (neutral palette: black, white, cream, camel, stone)
- Return rate under 8%
- Low category diversity
- Full price rate 65-75%
- Consideration arc 5-14 days

### Brand Loyalist
- Brand HHI above 0.65
- Under 5 unique brands visited in 30 days
- Full price rate 70-80%
- Return rate 8-14%
- Slow trend response speed

